WEBVTT

00:01.382 --> 00:03.315
That is a scary stack
of books.

00:04.162 --> 00:06.480
Does Mommy have
to read all those?

00:06.548 --> 00:08.849
Of course.
That's what you do

00:08.917 --> 00:10.217
when you go
to law school.

00:10.285 --> 00:11.919
Read books and
argue with people.

00:11.986 --> 00:13.253
Hey, what's going on?

00:13.304 --> 00:15.255
We suddenly having
a bowl shortage?

00:15.306 --> 00:17.424
We're just trying to save
our natural resources.

00:17.492 --> 00:19.643
This way, we only have
to wash the spoons.

00:21.128 --> 00:22.796
Okay, girls, shut that off.

00:22.864 --> 00:24.681
Grab your homework. Bedtime.

00:29.871 --> 00:31.338
Hello.

00:31.406 --> 00:34.608
Yes, hi.
I'm looking for a young college coed.

00:34.676 --> 00:36.777
A law student named
Allison Dubois?

00:36.844 --> 00:38.612
Smooth, Joe College.

00:38.680 --> 00:40.781
So, are you on the plane yet?

00:40.848 --> 00:42.849
Yes, we just boarded.

00:42.917 --> 00:45.669
Hey, listen, I wanted to try
one more time to convince you

00:45.753 --> 00:48.088
that you don't need to
pick me up in the morning.

00:48.155 --> 00:51.041
I think you should focus on
your first day of school.

00:51.125 --> 00:52.793
Well, that's awful thoughtful
of you, Daddy,

00:52.860 --> 00:55.796
but it's been six days since
I've laid eyes on you.

00:55.863 --> 00:58.298
I can't wait to see that tan
that you got in Hawaii.

00:58.366 --> 01:01.268
Hawaii?
Is that where I was?

01:01.335 --> 01:03.437
All I remember is the inside
of a military base.

01:03.504 --> 01:04.688
Hey, girls, it's Daddy.

01:04.772 --> 01:06.373
You want to say good night?

01:06.441 --> 01:07.841
Night, Dad!
See ya tomorrow!

01:07.892 --> 01:08.875
Love you, Daddy!

01:08.943 --> 01:10.410
Sweet dreams.

01:10.478 --> 01:11.612
Did you get that?

01:11.679 --> 01:14.081
Loud and clear.
I'll see you in the morning.

01:14.148 --> 01:19.253
Yep. I'll be the one who looks
like a first-year law student.

