01:28.413 --> 01:29.563
Hello.

01:29.631 --> 01:31.131
Hey, it's me.

01:31.199 --> 01:34.101
I'm sorry to call so early.
We picked up a tailwind,

01:34.168 --> 01:36.536
so we're landing at 5:00
instead of 6:00.

01:36.604 --> 01:38.872
So I already called
for the car service,

01:38.940 --> 01:41.174
so you just go back to sleep.

01:41.242 --> 01:45.112
Honey? Honey, what?
I just lost you for a second.

01:45.179 --> 01:46.780
Sorry.

01:46.881 --> 01:49.583
We just hit some turbulence
or something. Hold on, babe.

01:49.651 --> 01:51.485
PILOT
At this time I'm going

01:51.552 --> 01:53.186
to ask you to fasten
your seatbelts.

01:53.237 --> 01:54.821
Joe, what's going on?
Is everything okay?

01:54.889 --> 01:56.723
Uh, everything's fine, sweetie.

01:56.791 --> 02:00.027
Just a little bumpy.

02:01.195 --> 02:04.364
Joe, what's going on?
Talk to me!

02:04.415 --> 02:08.535
I love you, Allison!
I love you very...!

02:11.739 --> 02:14.141
Joe! Joe, Joe?!

